nk" href="https://www.thivien.net/Ng%C3%B4-Th%C3%AC-Nh%E1%BA%ADm/S%C6%A1n-pha-quy-m%C3%A3/poem-CwQAqI_uKX2Ak7i2uo48zA">Sơn pha quy mã - 山坡歸馬</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Ng%C3%B4-Th%C3%AC-Nh%E1%BA%ADm/author-14GcnhLjD2ajP0MTgtX13Q">Ngô Thì Nhậm</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/T%C3%A2n-ch%C3%AD/poem-q0JwbWHZ5RNvB8dXfxjizQ">Tân chí - 賓至</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Du/Th%C3%A1i-B%C3%ACnh-m%E1%BA%A1i-ca-gi%E1%BA%A3/poem-P3j-hu2ra9AUTYc_k_oguQ">Thái Bình mại ca giả - 太平賣歌者</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Du/author-ZRyB2U-4oqfhcjZ7xrf1_A">Nguyễn Du</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/Thi%E1%BA%BFu-ni%C3%AAn-h%C3%A0nh-M%C3%A3-th%C6%B0%E1%BB%A3ng-thu%E1%BB%B3-gia-b%E1%BA%A1c-m%E1%BB%8B-lang/poem-faBwcxekfvxLEHut3nsm4A">Thiếu niên hành (Mã thượng thuỳ gia bạc mị lang) - 少年行（馬上誰家薄媚郎）</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br></div>	</div>
